ent, indeed of enjoyment at all, by wheel-less users is clearly</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">demonstrated by the example of those limited parts of the Ridgeway which have been closed to vehicular traffic year round and which are now enjoyed and available to foot travellers in a manner not seen for years.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">In discussion with the Local Authority it is clear that they consider that the law as it stands makes it difficult for the Authority to close such byeways to off-roaders, whilst the cost of maintenance as a result of off-road activity is huge.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Please give the Local Authorities the tools with which to deal with this menace and to enhance the enjoyment of rights of way by the great majority of users.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">September 2013</span></p><div style="width:auto; height:21.85pt; float:left;"><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="RAMFooter2"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">2</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> of </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">1</span></a></p></div><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>